hadow_runs_since_transition||0))}</span><spanclass="font-semibold text-slate-800">자동 반영실행:</span><span>${escapeHtml(String(history.bounded_ema_runs_since_transition||0))}</span></div>${action?`<pclass="mt-2 text-[11px] text-amber-700">최근 전환: ${escapeHtml(prettyTransitionAction(action))} ·${escapeHtml(reason||"-")}</p>`:`<p class="mt-2 text-[11px] text-slate-500">아직 자동 전환 이력이 없습니다.</p>`}
